sequenceDiagram
    participant CP as CP
    participant G as GlbCtrl
    participant R as Router
    participant C as ClusCtrl
    participant Core as Core

    CP->>G: 下发 kernel reg info / packet
    G->>G: 解析 gridDim / clusDim / cta_num
    G->>G: 计算 max_clus_num / cluster mask
    G->>R: 广播 reg info 到目标 physical cluster
    R->>C: 转发 reg info
    G->>R: 分发 logic cluster index
    C->>Core: 拆成 block 后派给 core
    Core-->>C: block release / response
    C-->>G: cluster ack / response
    G-->>CP: kernel_done + kernel index
